{"tid":1794400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奧燒未燒完 中國逼使阿仙奴炒人 若奧斯爾不再上陣　將復播阿仙奴","createTime":"2019-12-23T05:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T15:30:45.000Z","uid":165683,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"fa2c390350e11311c4be578ae95b0f06ca075674","tid":1794400,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T05:37:09.000Z","msg":"效力英超阿仙奴的德國球員奧斯爾，早前發表聲援中國新疆維吾爾人的言論之後，內地中央電視台取消直播阿仙奴對曼城的賽事。<br />\n<br />\n在過去星期六，阿仙奴主場與愛華頓賽和0:0的賽事，賽前公布的陣容中，未有包括奧斯爾。根據體育頻道ESPN報道，央視突然在網上直播這場賽事，只提供英語旁述。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述央視的消息指出，若果阿仙奴由今個星期四對般尼茅夫的賽事開始，不再派出奧斯爾上陣，央視將會繼續播放阿仙奴的賽事。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴領隊龍格堡早前表示，奧斯爾未有被列入對愛華頓的賽事，因為狀態不足，以及上一場對曼城的賽事態度有問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499117-20191223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499117-20191223.htm&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=bb2e71d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499117-20191223.htm&h=14329958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499117-20191223.htm</a>"},{"pid":"36884e570f01f92773718e27e66387947969ee00","tid":1794400,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T05:49:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"97d98798b277f39c32c063af8b9fc5e0c666de9a","tid":1794400,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T05:54:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"13bdaff8621b94cc9a141d9564598af459b590f0","tid":1794400,"uid":272603,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T05:55:23.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新德國聯署</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"col